data.description: Move-in ready 5 bedroom 2 full bathroom with main level living, heat pump, replacement windows and many other recent updates! Main level features large living room, eat-in kitchen with hickory cabinets, granite countertops and stainless steel appliances, master bedroom full bathroom, guest bedroom and laundry/mud room! Upstairs you will find 3 more bedrooms and a large full bathroom with double sinks! Other features include refinished hardwoods throughout, replacement windows, heat pump and the list goes on! Outside you will find a nice covered front porch, rear covered patio, metal roof, nice flat yard for enjoyment and so much more! Don't miss out on this move-in ready home in a convenient location in the Town of Hillsville with many recent updates and public utilities!
